steps.text: This is your organization settings page. Depending on your user role, you will be able to update the organization's name, view payment information, and make new payments.
This is your teams page. Here you will be able to view all the teams you are on and create new teams.
This is your users page. As an administrator, you can delete a user from the organization instead of just a single team here.
As a Graphite Pro user, you can now easily share documents and files with your team.
You now also have access to Graphite Forms. You can create individual forms or forms that your entire team can access.
